{
  "stem": "10283.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So finally, we had this cousin, [NON-ENGLISH], in Cuba.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she wrote that she can get visas for us if we send the money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So then they did the right-- they sent the money to her address, and she supposedly got us visas, but only for my parents and me, and my-- not for my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we decided that at this point, we are not-- we cannot help it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're going to leave the grandparents back in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we got passage on the Saint Louis from the Hamburg America line for the 13th of May in 1939.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was from November the until May it took to get all this straightened out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the meantime, we had moved to a very small place [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and sold a lot of our belongings and just kept what we were going to take along.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we packed [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what they called a lift.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just great big wooden crates, but heavy-- heavier than crates.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were in [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] square.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were like-- like closets today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we packed everything in there that we were allowed to take in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before that, we had to bring all the jewelry and all the silver and everything to a certain place to give to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were allowed two settings a person to take along, that's all, two silver settings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while we were packing, an official from the government came to the house to watch that we didn't put anything into this-- into this lift other than household goods and dishes and things like that.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
